text: WNED may refer to: * WNED-FM, a radio station (94.5 FM) licensed to serve Buffalo, New York, United States * WNED-TV, a television station (channel 17 analog/43 digital) licensed to serve Buffalo, New York * WDCZ, a radio station (970 AM) licensed to serve Buffalo, New York, which held the call sign WNED from 1993 to 2012
title: WNED
